fulltitle: Dr. Billy Taylor on Improvisation, Jazz History, and Music Appreciation
description: In this previously unreleased lecture/demonstration from the Kennedy Center archives, jazz legends Dr. Billy Taylor (1921-2010) discusses jazz improvisation and performs solo piano pieces. Be sure to watch to the end to see up close footage of Dr. Taylor playing.
